rComments: Super accommodating with a generous heart. Keen to support students towards success. Has an excellent knowledge base about the field and research. Every class was filled with invaluable insights and reflections. Just loved his manner and approach to taking up critical issues and leaving us with more to think about. Great guy, great prof!

One of the best professors I've had. Although there is a lot of reading involved in his courses, he tries his best to break the ideas down and ensure that you are able to understand them. He manages to engage all of his students in thought-provoking discussions and activities. He's incredibly intelligent, funny, passionate, and a wonderful human.
Excellent and inspiring educator. Introduces you to many perspectives you may not have otherwise considered. Most students' research topics transformed after taking his class, for the better.

Amazing professor. One of the best I've ever had. He tries to incorporation participation in lectures, and you will feel inspired to participate. He is so knowledgeable and thoughtful and critical. I could not stop listening, even for a moment, when I was in his lectures. Fantastic. If you get a chance to take a class with him, be sure to take it.
A great pro. Very inspiring. Always ready to respond to your emails.
